Our mission is to provide our customers the chemicals they need to run their business’ successfully.  We do this through providing QUALITY PRODUCTS, SERVICE and FLEXIBILITY that is unmatched in the industry.  We will continue to expand our supply lines and pricing competitiveness, while operating our business in a SAFE AND SOUND manner.



Our Mission
Our Mission is to manufacture, distribute and sell high quality chemical, life science and consumer products to meet customers’ requirements.


Vision
To be the market leader in the "Pharmaceutical excipients & Fine Chemicals domain" with a Global perspective by exceeding Customer expectations in Quality and Service, attain operational excellence in Manufacturing, Total Quality Management, Safety & Supply Chain facilitated through our fully compliant state-of-the-art manufacturing plant.


We are committed to create a work culture that encourage trust in the organisation, respect to an individual and value the diversity in the organisation.